message.msgstr: On this page, you can enable/disable visit web through wan, you can not visit web through wan if you disable remote control, and you can visit web through wan if you enable remote control.
On this page, you can enable/disable WEB access through wan only by https.
On this page, you can enable/disable Https, and restart to be effective.
And you could configure web communication port(HTTP), and restart to be effective.
The configuration you have modifyed will be effective after reboot.
Please input a value of the port!
